Package com.day.cq.mcm.emailprovider.types

Interface Account

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseType, NamedType
    public interface Account
extends NamedType
    Defines an interface about an Account available with the email provider for a particular client. The Account interface has setter and getter methods for account identifier (id) and an account name (name). These are inherited from NamedType.

      • Methods inherited from interface com.day.cq.mcm.emailprovider.types.BaseType

        addParam, getId, getParam, getParams, setId, setParams

      • Methods inherited from interface com.day.cq.mcm.emailprovider.types.NamedType

        getName, setName
